  "text": "Samples collected from the receiver chamber were detected and the apparent permeability coefficients (Papp) were calculated. The absorption and transport of the drug in Caco-2 cell monolayer was evaluated by Papp. Propranolol and atenolol are typical drugs with high and low permeability on the Caco-2 cell monolayer. The Papp of propranolol and atenolol measured in this study were, respectively, (26.1ňė1.2)ňÜ10¬ī6 and (0.48ňė0.07)ňÜ10¬ī6 cm¬®s¬ī1, which was coincident with the literature [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
